      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains immaculate with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history and no performance issues whatsoever. Buyers can expect a collector-grade vehicle that needs absolutely nothing but a new home.",
