    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or a source for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including several large dents, rusted panels, and peeling clear coat. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips, meaning it will likely require a tow rather than being driven home. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is, with no warranties expressed or implied.",
